{
  "stem": "3382.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said in German, if I have to die, so I can die without it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, he said, put him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So a soldier came up to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at that moment, came up Krzanowski, and said to the officer something-- whispered something in the ear.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Let him go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] they didn't touch anybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They went on the trucks and moved away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I came up to Krzanowki, I told him, you [INAUDIBLE]-- what did you tell him that suddenly he change?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, very simple.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said that you are married to a Jewish woman.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, obviously, if you are married to a Jewish woman, you wouldn't do it-- you wouldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You are innocent.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, do you know that if I write a Jewish woman, I am liable to be shot?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is the official thing?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yes, so run away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So, you know, so I run back, you know-- back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I took some more valuables.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I put certain things-- I had-- I bought a pair of German boots with-- German boots were that had on the soles nails.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But in between here, I stuck in some golden pieces that were hidden in other pieces.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the other pieces, I stuck in all the documents, you know, and ran out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I took-- look, look, I told him, I'm going to [NON-ENGLISH], that means, you know, where supposing my wife is.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But-- oh, and you will get tomorrow, the horse you will get at [NON-ENGLISH] What I did, what I thought, if I leave somewhere, I tell him I'll go kilometer or two.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I turn around the horse, and then run across the fields and some swamps, you know, to Rulewicze.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
